column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: TRIDENT SOFT GUM STRAWBERRY SUGAR FREE, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 00000050098781
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

INGREDIENTS: Sweeteners (sorbitol, maltitol syrup, maltitol, xylitol, aspartame, sucralose, acesulfame K), gum base, humectant (glycerol), flavourings, emulsifiers (sunflower lecithin, E472a), acids (citric, malic), colour (cochineal), antioxidant (E321). Excessive consumption may produce laxative effects. Contains a source of phenylalanine.. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 09/26/2016
